# Future Vision (Образ будущего) — Business Logic

> **Truth order:** code + `libs/shared-types` + Mongoose schemas + tRPC → sprint notes / PRD → other drafts.
>
> **Scope:** the **`future-vision` priority hub community** (`typeTag === 'future-vision'`), **OB publications** inside it (`sourceEntityType === 'community'`), **`communities.getFutureVisions`**, and **per-community `futureVision*` fields** on ordinary communities. Not to be confused with cooperative **project** communities (`isProject`) — see @business-projects.mdc.

