## Data model

### On **source** `Community` (team, custom, …)

| Field | Role |
|-------|------|
| `futureVisionText` | Required for OB narrative; drives OB post **content** |
| `futureVisionTags` | String array; feed filter + UI pills |
| `futureVisionCover` | URL; card cover |

### In **`future-vision` hub** — `Publication` (OB post)

Created by `PublicationService.createFutureVisionPost`:

| Field | Value |
|-------|--------|
| `communityId` | Hub id (`getCommunityByTypeTag('future-vision')`) |
| `sourceEntityId` | Source community id |
| `sourceEntityType` | `'community'` |
| `postType` | `'basic'` |
| `content` | From `futureVisionText` |
| `postCost` | Effectively none (system create; no fee path) |

Updates: `updateFutureVisionPostContent` — **content only**, **no** edit-window check; votes/comments/rating unchanged.

Lookup: `findFutureVisionPostId(hubId, sourceCommunityId)`.

### Platform settings

| Field | Role |
|-------|------|
| `availableFutureVisionTags` | Superadmin-managed list for filters / forms (default `[]` in bootstrap) |

