## Tags rubric

- **Storage:** `platformSettings.availableFutureVisionTags` (array). Decree 809 lists live in `decree809Enabled` / `decree809Tags` (see platform settings schema).
- **Mutation:** `platformSettings.updateFutureVisionTags` (superadmin; see router).
- **Usage:** **Feed tag UI** merges Decree 809 (when enabled) and admin extras via `buildEffectiveRubricatorSections`. **Server-side feed filter** still matches only each source community’s stored `futureVisionTags` against the selected tags (intersection; see [Feed](#future-visions-feed)). Create-community forms use `availableFutureVisionTags` for suggestions.

